=== Starting CrowdSec Guardian ===
  [FAIL] Could not start service: Failed to start service 'CrowdSec Guardian (CrowdSec)'.

  Troubleshooting steps:
  1. Check service logs:
     Get-Content 'C:\ProgramData\CrowdSec\log\service_stderr.log'
     Get-Content 'C:\ProgramData\CrowdSec\log\service_stdout.log'
  2. Test crowdsec.exe manually:
     cd 'C:\Program Files\CrowdSec'
     .\crowdsec.exe --config 'C:\ProgramData\CrowdSec\config\config.yaml'
  3. Check Windows Event Log:
     Get-EventLog -LogName System -Source 'Service Control Manager' -Newest 10
  4. Try starting manually:
     nssm start CrowdSec


